OL,3,CTenants facing 'nightmare' as council-
OL,4,Crun housing company could close
OL,6,FITV News Meridian's Mel Bloor reports.
OL,8,FReading Borough Council's proposals to
OL,9,Fclose its 'Homes for Reading' have
OL,10,Fbeen described as a 'nightmare' by
OL,11,Fresidents, as more than 100 face
OL,12,Flosing their tenancies.
OL,14,FThe council-owned company could be
OL,15,Fwound down due to pressures on the
OL,16,Fauthorities finances, meaning the
OL,17,Fproperties it owns would be added to
OL,18,Fthe council's existing stock.
