OL,6,FThis process would then see the homes
OL,7,Fre-let as council homes, with a focus
OL,8,Fon letting them to key workers.
OL,10,FBut for those who thought they would
OL,11,Fhave a stable, long-term home, it is
OL,12,Fof little consolation.
