OL,4,Crun housing company could close
OL,6,FThe council says people will be able
OL,7,Fto remain in their properties until
OL,8,Ftheir tenancies expire, some of which
OL,9,Frun up to 2026 and it will help them
OL,10,Ffind alternative accommodation.
OL,12,FIt is considering winding down the
OL,13,Fcompany due to changes to local
OL,14,Fauthority lending rules, the housing
OL,15,Fmarket, interest rates on borrowing,
OL,16,Fand other external factors in recent
OL,17,Fyears which have affected the
OL,18,Fpotential viability of the company in
OL,19,Fthe long term.
