OL,6,FThe authority also highlighted the
OL,7,Fdifficult financial position it is
OL,8,Fcurrently in, and said it was unable
OL,9,Fto absorb any financial risk or losses.
OL,11,FJohn Knight, Interim Director of
OL,12,FHousing at Reading Borough Council,
OL,13,Ftold ITV Meridian the authority will
OL,14,Fdo it can to ensure those affected if
OL,15,Fthe company is wound down will still
OL,16,Fhave a home in the town.J"We've got
OL,17,Fvery successful schemes to offer
OL,18,Falternative accommodation to people
OL,19,Fincluding the private sector", he said.
