OL,6,F"So we'll work with people to assess
OL,7,Ftheir situation including their
OL,8,Ffinances and try and get them
OL,9,Falternative accommodation well before
OL,10,Fthe time they are actually facing
OL,11,Fhomelessness."
OL,13,FWarnings have continued over the
OL,14,Fperilous state of council finances and
OL,15,Ffrontline services being under threat
OL,16,Fdespite the Government recently making
OL,17,Fan additional #600 million available
OL,18,Fin the local government finance
OL,19,Fsettlement.
