OL,6,FAn LGA survey of council chief
OL,7,Fexecutives found 85% of local
OL,8,Fauthorities continue to plan
OL,9,Freductions in spending on key services
OL,10,Fas the sector faces a funding gap of
OL,11,F#4 billion over the next two years.
OL,13,FResidents affected now have to wait
OL,14,Funtil April when the council is set to
OL,15,Fmake a decision on the future of the
OL,16,Fhomes.
